result.execSummary:
On one or more charges, the deferred prosecution or sentencing agreement(s) on this case were fulfilled, and the charge(s) were dismissed.

The defendant Elizabeth A. Tietsort was found guilty of the following charge(s) in this case. One or more other charges in this case were dismissed. The dismissed charges were not proven and have no legal effect. Elizabeth A. Tietsort is presumed innocent of the dismissed charges.

  • Elizabeth A. Tietsort was found guilty of Intentionally Abuse Hazardous Substance, a class A misdemeanor, Wisconsin Statutes 941.316(2)(b).
